    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >毛线圈</h2>包裹、编织和缠绕你的毛线！一丝一缕、每次一圈，在这款展现匠人精神的宁静游戏中打造艺术之作。从现有关卡的大型展览中汲取灵感，在令人松弛的配乐中放松自我。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878910/extras/14a35fe85672c839aa91e2170e1e5ca0.poster.avif?t=1772128133\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878910/extras/14a35fe85672c839aa91e2170e1e5ca0.webm?t=1772128133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878910/extras/14a35fe85672c839aa91e2170e1e5ca0.mp4?t=1772128133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2>《毛线圈》是一款创意游戏。通过拖拽纱线一圈圈地缠绕在画布上各式各样的大头针上，你可以打造出绝佳的艺术之作。慢慢地，每次一根线，图形将会逐渐呈现，直至最终，构成一幅美妙的编织大作。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878910/extras/e6f1645caea2553e2cfe152b2fe92984.poster.avif?t=1772128133\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878910/extras/e6f1645caea2553e2cfe152b2fe92984.webm?t=1772128133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878910/extras/e6f1645caea2553e2cfe152b2fe92984.mp4?t=1772128133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新游戏+</h2>您可以使用 新游戏+[ 重播机制解锁每个级别的定制。各种颜色适用于每根绳子！获得创意，受到启发，或者只是古怪！你会做什么？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878910/extras/f6da0aab5ae4e8a5ccf95f5971352986.poster.avif?t=1772128133\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878910/extras/f6da0aab5ae4e8a5ccf95f5971352986.webm?t=1772128133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >放松</h2>从开始到结束，毛线圈 旨在让您放松身心并获得奖励，以帮助您放松身心。绝对一切都是轻松的，音乐，游戏玩法，即使你犯了一个错误！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878910/extras/29b8b5c65873c7da57defb1035b63fb8.poster.avif?t=1772128133\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878910/extras/29b8b5c65873c7da57defb1035b63fb8.webm?t=1772128133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878910/extras/29b8b5c65873c7da57defb1035b63fb8.mp4?t=1772128133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由</h2>免费提供",
